            <p>The following Privacy Policy discloses our approach in gathering and processing Personal Data for Online Media Technologies&nbsp;Ltd. website www.avs4you.com, related websites, services and AVS4YOU software.</p>
            <p>Any data collected through avs4you.com, forum.avs4you.com or www.avs4you.com and other subdomains of the domain avs4you.com (collectively the “AVS4YOU Website”) or AVS Video Editor, AVS Video Converter, AVS Video ReMaker, AVS Audio Editor, AVS Audio Converter, AVS Image Converter, AVS Document Converter, AVS Media Player, AVS Registry Cleaner, AVS Disc Creator, AVS Photo Editor (collectively the “AVS4YOU Software”) will be collected by Online Media Technologies&nbsp;Ltd. which is a company formed in London, UK with its principal place of business located at 85 Great Portland, London W1W 7LT, United Kingdom.</p>
            <p>By using AVS4YOU Website or Software (hereinafter also referred to as “AVS4YOU”) you explicitly consent to such use of your Personal Data and agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>
            <p>We process data based on:</p>
