                <br />Please visit the link to understand Google's approach to privacy: https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en</p>
            <h3>Privacy Policy Updates</h3>
            <p>Online Media Technologies&nbsp;Ltd. may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this privacy statement for any changes occasionally. If any changes are made to the way in which we treat your Personal Data, we will inform you about such changes via email or by posting a note on our website.</p>
